()SailPoint IdentityNow ek cloud-based IAM (Identity and Access Management) platform hai.
Simple words me:-
IdentityNow ek system hai jo company me
users ko kaunsa application access milega
ye control karta hai.

1️⃣ IdentityNow kya karta hai?
Ye company me user access manage karta hai.
Example:-
Employee → Rahul
Applications → Salesforce, SAP, Jira

()IdentityNow decide karega:-
Rahul ko kaun sa access milega
kaun approve karega
kab revoke hoga

6️⃣ IdentityNow ka main purpose
Right user
Right access
Right time
Matlab:-
Galat user ko access nahi milega

()Flow:-
Rahul
↓
Access Request
↓
Manager Approval
↓
IdentityNow
↓
Salesforce access mil gaya

3️⃣ IdentityNow kya manage karta hai
IdentityNow ye sab manage karta hai:-
Identities (users)
Accounts
Entitlements
Access Profiles
Roles
Access Requests
Approvals
Provisioning


1️⃣ Identity:-
Identity = User / Employee
Example:-
Rahul
Amit
Priya
Identity ke attributes ho sakte hain:-
firstname
lastname
email
department
manager

Example:-
Name: Rahul
Department: IT
Email: rahul@company.com

2️⃣ Source:-
Source = System jahan se user data aata hai
Examples:-
Active Directory
HR system
Database
Salesforce

Flow:-
HR System
   ↓
IdentityNow Source
   ↓
Identity create

3️⃣ Aggregation:-
Aggregation = Source se users aur accounts import karna
Example:-
Active Directory
      ↓
Aggregation
      ↓
IdentityNow me users load

4️⃣ Identity Profile:-
Identity Profile = Identity create karne ka rule
Ye decide karta hai:-
kaun sa source use hoga
kaun se attributes identity me aayenge
Example mapping:-
HR.firstName → Identity.firstName
HR.email → Identity.email

5️⃣ Transform:-
Transform = Data modify karna
Example:-
firstname + lastname → displayName
Example output:-
Rahul + Kumar = Rahul Kumar

6️⃣ Role:-
Role = Access ka group
Example:-
Finance Role
IT Admin Role
HR Role
Role me multiple permissions hote hain.

Example:-
Finance Role
   ↓
SAP access
Database access

7️⃣ Access Profile:-
Access Profile = Application access ka package
Example:-
Application: SAP
Access Profile: SAP Finance Access

8️⃣ Entitlement:-
Entitlement = Specific permission
Example:-
SAP_READ
SAP_WRITE
ADMIN_ACCESS

9️⃣ Lifecycle State:-
Lifecycle State = User ka status
Example:-
Joiner
Active
Leave

Flow:-
Employee Join
      ↓
Joiner State
      ↓
Access assign

🔟 Provisioning:-
Provisioning = Access create / update / remove
Example:-
User request SAP access
        ↓
Provisioning
        ↓
SAP account create
1️⃣1️⃣ Access Request

User khud access request karta hai.

Example:

Rahul requests SAP access
Manager approves
Access granted

1️⃣2️⃣ Access Certification:-
Access review process
Manager check karta hai:-
Employee ko ye access chahiye ya nahi
Example:-
Manager Review
   ↓
Keep / Remove access

1️⃣3️⃣ Governance:-
Security aur compliance manage karna
Example:-
Policy
Access Review
Audit
---------------------------------------------------
🔹 Complete IdentityNow Flow:-
HR System / Active Directory (Source)
            ↓
        Aggregation
            ↓
        Identity Profile
            ↓
        Identity Create
            ↓
        Transform
            ↓
        Role Assignment
            ↓
        Access Profile
            ↓
        Entitlement
            ↓
        Access Request
            ↓
        Approval Workflow
            ↓
        Provisioning
            ↓
        Application Access
            ↓
        Access Certification
            ↓
        Governance / Audit
---------------------------------------------
